spec_data.Name: perl-Module-Build-XSUtil
spec_data.Description:
Module::Build::XSUtil is a subclass of Module::Build to support building XS
modules. It adds a number of compiler-related optional parameters to
Module::Build's "new" method.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:27:58 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A Module::Build class for building XS modules
